## Component-Based UI
React is a JavaScript library for building user interfaces. It uses **components** to break complex UIs into small, reusable pieces.

```jsx
// A functional component
function Welcome(props) {
  return <h1>Hello, {props.name}</h1>;
}

// Using the component
function App() {
  return (
    <div>
      <Welcome name="Alice" />
      <Welcome name="Bob" />
    </div>
  );
}
```

JSX allows you to write HTML-like syntax inside JavaScript.

